<plot>After 9/11 many began questioning the idea of a Muslim youth camp. There was fear that such camps would be used to train terrorists and teach young Muslims hatred towards Christians and Jews. This film follows a group of young American Muslims who travel to a Muslim Camp in California and explores their different social, religious and political views and answers the question: what really goes on in a Muslim youth camp?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?091972</url></doc>
